Looking for an everyday bank account?



Our Select account comes with all the essentials that make banking easy.


Apply now


 
To apply you must be 18 or over and a UK resident.














  



Our apps just keeps on
getting better


With your new app update you can now make international payments on your iPad and be greeted personally at each login on your mobile device.


See what’s updated in our app


 
App available on most smartphones to Royal Bank Of Scotland customers with Digital Banking and a UK mobile number














  



First time buyers get £500 cashback


Rather spend money on something enjoyable for your new home? Of course you would!
That's why when you take out a first time buyer exclusive mortgage with us, you'll get £500 cashback, paid directly to your solicitor on the day of drawdown of the mortgage.


More on our cashback offer



Offer can be changed or withdrawn at any time. Early repayment charges may apply. Max LTV 90%.
Your home may be repossessed if you do not keep up repayments on your mortgage.
 


















  



Why dial when you 
can tap


Lost or damaged your card?
Order a replacement card online in less than 2 minutes.


How do I do it?
















  



Have an unexpected bill?


Whether you have an unexpected bill to pay or would like a safety net just incase, an arranged overdraft could help you keep it covered!

Available to customers with eligible current accounts who are aged 18 and over. Overdraft usage fees apply.


Apply Today 
















  



Do you know who’s calling? 


 
Fraudsters call pretending to be the bank and other companies  you know.
If you receive a call out the blue, take five minutes to check what’s being asked, by phoning a number  you trust. 


Avoid phone scams


 
 



























