Digital Banking
Manage your account, any time any day

Log in now


Setup Digital Banking




Digital Banking available to customers aged 11+ with an Royal Bank of Scotland account.
















                            Forgotten your PIN or Password








                            Our latest update to Digital Banking








                            Our Secure Banking Promise








                            Free Rapport security software








                            Do more with Digital Banking








                            Help & Support
























We've added international payments into our mobile app!




Thank you for choosing to bank with us through Digital Banking.
We want to let you know that we have added the ability to pay your international payees from Digital Banking in the mobile app to make banking even easier.


Find out more


App available to customers with Digital Banking and a UK mobile number. Payments must be made on Digital Banking before you can pay through our app.







Person using mobile phone

















